{"article_id":"fhe4h6BpJaA1uT0q","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump has said","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"the US will inflict `` severe punishment '' on Saudi Arabia","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"if the kingdom is found to be responsible for the death of journalist Jamal Khashoggi .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"He said","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"he would be `` very upset and angry","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"if that were the case '' ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"but ruled out halting big military contracts .","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"Mr Khashoggi , a critic of the Saudi government , vanished on 2 October","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"after visiting its consulate in Istanbul .","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"Saudi Arabia dismissed allegations","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"that it ordered his killing","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"as `` lies '' .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"The interior minister said on Friday","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"that the kingdom was keen to uncover `` the whole truth '' ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"stressing","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"reports `` about orders","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"to kill ''","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"are `` baseless '' .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"A Turkish security source has told the BBC","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"that officials had audio and video evidence","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"proving","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Mr Khashoggi ,","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"who writes for the Washington Post ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"was murdered inside the consulate .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"The country 's Foreign Minister , Mevut Cavusoglu , said","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"Saudi Arabia was not yet co-operating with the investigation .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"He urged it to do so","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"and allow Turkish officials to enter the consulate .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"In an interview with CBS News , Mr Trump said","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"that , if true ,","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"the fact","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"that a journalist was murdered","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"was `` terrible and disgusting '' .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"`` We 're going to get to the bottom of it","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"and there will be severe punishment , ''","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"`` As of this moment , they deny it vehemently .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"Could it be them ?","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Yes , ''","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"he added .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"However , he said","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"that there were `` other ways of punishing ''","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"than cancelling military contracts ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"which powers like Russia and China were interested in .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"`` I do n't want to hurt jobs ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"I do n't want to lose an order like that , ''","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Mr Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Speaking to journalists later ,","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Mr Trump said","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"his first hope had been that Mr Khashoggi was not killed ,","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"but `` maybe that is not looking good '' .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"He would probably call Saudi King Salman `` tonight or tomorrow '' ,","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"he added .","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"On Friday UN Secretary General Antonio Guterres told the BBC","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"that `` this kind of incident is multiplying ''","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"and urged the international community to respond .","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"that ,","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"once it was clear what had happened to Mr Khashoggi ,","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"governments should decide `` in the appropriate way '' whether to attend an investment conference","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"to be held in the Saudi capital Riyadh this month .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Jim Kim , the head of the World Bank , has already withdrawn from the event .","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"Sir Richard Branson , the head of Virgin , has said","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"he is suspending his role as director of two tourism projects .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"He has also halted discussions about a $ 1bn","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"( £750m )","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"investment by the Saudi sovereign wealth fund into Virgin 's space ventures .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"The latest reports suggest","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"an assault and a struggle took place in the consulate .","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"A Turkish security source has confirmed to BBC Arabic the existence of an audio and a video recording .","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"What is not clear is if anyone other than Turkish officials has seen or heard them .","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"On Saturday Turkish pro-government newspaper Sabah said","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"the audio recording came from an Apple Watch","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"Mr Khashoggi was wearing at the time .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"The recording was recovered from his iPhone ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"which he gave to his Turkish fiancée Hatice Cengiz","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"when he entered the consulate ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"and his iCloud account ,","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"the paper added .","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"However , it was not clear how the data could have been uploaded from the watch to iCloud .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"One source is quoted by the Washington Post","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"as saying","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"men can be heard beating Mr Khashoggi ;","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"it adds","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"that the recordings show","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"he was killed and dismembered .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"`` You can hear his voice and the voices of the men","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"speaking Arabic , ''","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"a separate source told the Post ,","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"which employed Mr Khashoggi as a contributing columnist .","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"`` You can hear how he was interrogated , tortured and then murdered . ''","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"Turkish TV has already broadcast CCTV footage of the moment","depth":4},{"id":92,"text":"Mr Khashoggi walked into the consulate for an appointment","depth":5},{"id":93,"text":"at which he was due to receive papers for his forthcoming marriage to Ms Cengiz .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":187,"left":121,"right":186,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":121,"left":100,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":96,"right":99,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":0,"right":95,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":95,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":98,"right":6,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":98,"left":3,"right":97,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":97,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":101,"right":119,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":109,"right":118,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":109,"left":103,"right":108,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":102,"right":11,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":102,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":12,"right":107,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":107,"left":13,"right":106,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":14,"right":105,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":105,"left":104,"right":17,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"paren